				<td colspan="2"><span>(apologies to Mad TV for that title)
<br />

<br />

<br />
I used to be under the misapprehension that prox aggro could occur only on a server tick... about once every six seconds.
<br />

<br />
But now I have evidence that it's much faster than that, more like every 2 seconds or less.
<br />

<br />
Anyone have the skinny on how this really works?</span></td>
