I think i got that impression from a Necro that had a Circlet of Shadows (instant click invis). The nec could get aggro, flop, and then stand clicking the circlet. Assuming the mob did'nt see invis the Nec would not regain aggro,if he clicked the circlet within a couple seconds of standing.
<br />

<br />
If anyone knows the actual mechanics of this then i am curious also.</span></td>
